<p>
	This mystical deck of tarot cards was created by the artist Luca Russo who illustrates how the world spins slowly beneath a dying sun, the Dark Angels descend to walk the wounded earth once again. Taking upon themselves the passions and desires of mankind, they witness the last, strange flowering of humanity as time itself spirals down into darkness.&nbsp;This fantastic deck of tarot cards comes with instructions and contains 78 Arcana cards of bitter hope and dark solace in the size of 64mm x 122mm.</p>
